'''Petrus Van Theemsche''' (15 August 1915 &ndash; 28 May 1999) was a Belgian [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]].<ref name="procyclingstats">{{cite web |url=http://www.procyclingstats.com/rider.php?id=173001 |title=Petrus Van Theemsche |accessdate=29 April 2014 |work=Pro Cycling Stats}}</ref> He won the [[Belgian National Road Race Championships|Belgian national road race title]] in 1938.<ref name="CyclingArchives">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/coureurfiche.php?coureurid=7850 |title=Petrus Van Theemsche |accessdate=29 April 2014 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref>

